  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can choose for your poison to not cause fatigue, instead causing it to alter the thought process of those subjected to it (this talent cannot be used with a contact or inhaled poison). Those who are under the effects of this poison can select a single Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma-based skill, gaining a +2 alchemical bonus to the next check they make with that skill within 1 minute. Those under the effects of this poison suffer a -5 penalty to Initiative checks for 1 minute. For every 5 ranks in Craft (alchemy) you possess, this bonus increases by +2. A creature cannot benefit from a Psychotropic Hallucinogen more than once per hour.</p>\n",
